{"id":20026,"type":2,"name":"IZUMO -猛き剣の閃記-","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/91/d5/20026_fF9rD.jpg","rating":{"total":69,"count":{"1":0,"2":3,"3":2,"4":9,"5":24,"6":19,"7":7,"8":3,"9":1,"10":1},"score":5.4},"summary":"《出云战记》是以Studio e.go!公司制作的游戏《IZUMO》为原作的电视动画。2005年4月至6月播放。 八岐猛是一个性格单纯又直率的少年。他的生活似乎从很小的时候就已经模式化了：每天早上被青梅竹马的白鸟姐妹里的明日香用各种飞身飞脚叫起床，然后再把姐姐琴乃做的早饭吃光，接着出门与幼年起的玩伴大斗刚打过招呼后匆忙上学。这样的生活已经千篇一律让人觉得没什么新奇可言了。\r\n\r\n然而在一场地震过后，八岐猛的校园生活就有了翻天覆地的彻底改变。学校顷刻间在地震中化为了废墟，随之出现的是一群恐怖的异形怪物，接着又从校舍中涌出了一群身着日本古代服装的奇怪人士——为了恢复现代社会的面貌，猛不得不开始了残酷的战斗……","info":"null","collection":{"wish":49,"collect":123,"doing":1,"on_hold":21,"dropped":21},"eps":[{"id":108909,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108909","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108910,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108910","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108911,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108911","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108912,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108912","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108913,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108913","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108914,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108914","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108915,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108915","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108916,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108916","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108917,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/108917","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":108918